title: Weekly Review Process
content:
# Weekly Review

1. Review completed tasks
2. Update progress on projects
3. Plan next week
4. Archive completed items

title: Monthly Financial Close
content:
# Monthly Close

1. Reconcile all accounts
2. Review expenses
3. Update budget tracking
4. Generate reports

title: Daily Standup
content:
# Standup

1. What did I do yesterday?
2. What will I do today?
3. Any blockers?

title: Quarterly Planning
content:
# Q1 Planning

1. Review last quarter results
2. Set OKRs
3. Allocate resources
4. Communicate plan
